ComicInfo.Summary:
It’s the showdown we’ve been building to… the Danger Dolls must face off with their genetically engineered offspring, Klustur Fukur, if they hope to escape the hellish alien world they’ve been stranded on!
Features artist and action figure variant covers (each with their own risqué variant as well)!
